request.description:
Login to get JWT token. For multi-tenant users, you'll receive a tenant list and need to call this again with tenantId.

**Example Request:**
```json
{
  "email": "admin@acme.com",
  "password": "password123"
}
```

**Example Response (200):**
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "data": {
    "token": "eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...",
    "user": {
      "id": "123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000",
      "email": "admin@acme.com",
      "role": "admin",
      "tenantId": "tenant-123"
    }
  }
}
```

**Example Response (Multi-tenant user):**
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "data": {
    "requiresTenantSelection": true,
    "tenants": [
      {
        "id": "tenant-123",
        "name": "Tenant 1"
      },
      {
        "id": "tenant-456",
        "name": "Tenant 2"
      }
    ]
  }
}
```

Login with tenant selection (for multi-tenant users). Use after receiving tenant list from initial login.

**Example Request:**
```json
{
  "email": "admin@acme.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "tenantId": "tenant-123"
}
```

**Example Response (200):**
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "data": {
    "token": "eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9...",
    "user": {
      "id": "123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000",
      "email": "admin@acme.com",
      "role": "admin",
      "tenantId": "tenant-123"
    }
  }
}
```

